    "measurementNotes": "Values are published mean CIELAB coordinates from peer-reviewed spectrophotometric/colorimetric studies of physical VITA shade guide tabs. sRGB previews in the demo are computed from these L*a*b* values and will differ from the physical tabs because of display calibration, gloss, translucency, and geometry.",
    "displayConversion": {
      "target": "sRGB",
      "method": "CIELAB → XYZ (D65) → linear sRGB → gamma encode"
    }
  },
